results.title: Cover #12397
results.description:
The Fantastic Four spring to action as a team for the first time. As they
learn how to control their new found powers, will it be enough to stop the
fury of the Mole Man???

results.title: The Fantastic Four!
results.description: Dr. Reed Richards takes his friends on a rocket trip that changes their lives forever.

results.title: The Fantastic Four Meet the Mole Men
results.description:
The Fantastic Four spring to action as a team for the first time. As they
learn how to control their new found powers, will it be enough to stop the
fury of the Mole Man?!!

results.title: The Moleman's Secret!
results.description: The first skirmish with the Moleman and his monsters.

results.title: The Return of Doctor Doom!
results.description: Doctor Doom returns from his unwanted journey in space and visits Jack Kirby and Stan Lee in order to make them set a trap for the Fantastic Four.

results.title: Part 2 "Back from the Dead!"
results.description: Doctor Doom tells how he managed to return to Earth with the help of the Ovoids and then he changes bodies with Mr Fantastic using Ovoid technology.

results.title: Part 3 "The End of Mr. Fantastic?"
results.description: Doctor Doom convinces the rest of the Fantastic Four that he is Mr Fantastic.

results.title: Part 4 "No Place to Turn!"
results.description: Doctor Doom (as Mr. Fantastic) displays his new shrinking-ray and Mr. Fantastic (in Doom's body) escapes his captivity in Doom's castle.

results.title: Part 5 "The Real Doctor Doom!"
results.description: Doctor Doom and Mr. Fantastic get their bodies back and Doom is put under his own shrinking-ray and shrinks down to sub-atomic size.
